episodes.title: How Do Cults Trap People?
episodes.description:
Are you drinking the Kool-aid? Join us on a visual journey into cults as we explore the tactics, philosophies, and psychologies of some real-life Joseph Seeds, the cult leader and antagonist of Far Cry 5. Far Cry 5 will be available on March 27 on PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and PC. Made possible by Far Cry 5.
